Public Funding in Germany as of January 2023

drfetz

2022-12-06

Preface

The present report deals with public funding in Germany. Only Verbundprojekte - projects with more than two participating entities - have been assessed. The data is publicly available via: https://foerderportal.bund.de/foekat/jsp/SucheAction.do.

Funding by ressort

BMBF = Bundesministerium fr Bildung und Forschung, Federal ministry of education and research; BMDV = Bundesministerium fr Digitales und Verkehr, Federal ministry of digital and transport; BMEL = Bundesministerium fr Ernhrung und Landwirtschaft, Federal ministry of food and agriculture; BMWK = Bundesministerium fr Wirtschaft und Klimaschutz, Federal ministry of economic affairs and climate action. According to the website, each ministry is individually responsible for providing accurate data.
